spas.nhandling.nelements

Class NElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • spas.nhandling.nelements.NElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NCourse, NEvent

    public class NElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Superclass for all different NElements. Organization and department types are made straight out of this class. Point for this class is to get an objet-type representation of all the information needed from the Noppa API.
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Lauri Lavanti
    See Also:
    NElementType
